Project: claudetrack
Task: Fix landing page auth-aware CTA buttons:

src/app/page.tsx is a server component that checks Supabase session.
src/app/landing-content.tsx is a client component.

The server component should:
1. Get user session with createServerSupabaseClient()
2. Pass isLoggedIn boolean to LandingContent

LandingContent should:
- If isLoggedIn=true: all CTA buttons (Get Started, Start Free Trial, Get Started Free) → /dashboard
- If isLoggedIn=false: → /auth/signup

Check current implementation and fix if not working correctly.
Run bun run build to confirm.

